HDO Pro

This repository is no longer the main home of HDO Pro.

HDO Pro originally started as a small project focused on improving the user experience with features such as:

* No Ads
* Faster Loading Times
* Reduced Interruptions
* Optimized Performance

Since then, the project has grown into its own community-driven project with its own identity and direction.

This repository represents an older version of the project from before the HDO Pro community rebrand and transition into an independent project.

Development is no longer maintained here.

Current repository:
https://github.com/HDO-PRO/hdo-pro](https://github.com/HDO-PRO/hdo-pro)

Note:
This repository is kept online for archival and historical purposes only. Updates, announcements, and future development take place in the current repository.

Thank you to everyone who supported HDO Pro throughout its development and growth.
